    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Do you think we should also add more generic ais-header, ais-footer classes everytime the decorator is called.\n\nYes we need so I believe.\n\nMost of the time all the headers of widgets have the same rendering.\n\nEven in our themes, not having it would mean that we would need to specify all the classes?\n",
