    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Without those classes, this would mean styling `ais-widget1--header, ais-widget2--header {}`. That might become painful really quick, you're right. I'll add them.\n\nI'm unsure we need to add `ais-root` and `ais-body`, though. Because those elements will only be added if the widget uses the `headerFooter` decorator. Not all widget will have them.\n",
